spell_list.description: A replacement for Harm Touch. This ability deals a great amount of disease damage to enemies surrounding the target. This attack can not be outright resisted. For a short duration after the attack, the shadowknight will transform into a netherlord and some of their area effect abilities will cast instantly.
spell_list.description_pvp: A replacement for Harm Touch. This ability deals a great amount of disease damage to enemies surrounding the target. This attack can not be outright resisted. For a short duration after the attack, the shadowknight will transform into a netherlord and some of their area effect abilities will cast instantly.

effect_list.description: Inflicts 64 - 106 disease damage on targets in Area of Effect
Applies Grim Reaper.  Lasts for 36.0 seconds.
Doom Judgment, Death Cloud, Chaos Cloud, Reaper's Mist and Unending Agony will cast instantly.

spell_list.name: Reaper's Touch
